---

<section class="about">
  <div class="hero">
    <span class="eyebrow">Sunrise Residential</span>
    <h1>Senior living with warmth, dignity, and community in Roseville, Minnesota.</h1>
    <p>
      At Sunrise Residential, we provide vibrant, compassionate assisted living in a welcoming neighborhood close to parks,
      shopping, and the heart of Roseville. Our team is dedicated to helping residents enjoy every day with independence and support.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid">
    <article>
      <h2>Our mission</h2>
      <p>
        We create an uplifting home where seniors are valued, supported, and enhanced through personalized care, meaningful connection,
        and thoughtful services.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2>Personalized care</h2>
      <p>
        Each resident has a tailored wellness plan designed around their needs, preferences, and routines.
        From daily assistance to medication reminders and mobility support, our team is ready 24/7.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2>Community life</h2>
      <p>
        Enjoy small-group activities, social dining, gentle fitness classes, arts and crafts, and neighborhood outings that
        promote friendship, purpose, and joy.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2>Roseville location</h2>
      <p>
        Sunrise Residential sits in the heart of a friendly Minnesota community near parks, lakes, medical services, and local shops.
        Our location makes it easy for families to visit and residents to stay connected to the city they love.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="callout">
    <div>
      <h2>Why families trust Sunrise Residential</h2>
      <p>
        Our home is built on respect, transparency, and thoughtful attention. We partner with each family to ensure comfort,
        confidence, and peace of mind.
      </p>
    </div>
    <a href="/" class="button">Schedule a tour</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 1040px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px 24px;
    font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    color: #111827;
  }

  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0 16px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #7c3aed;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 2.5vw, 3.25rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 850px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .hero p {
    margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
    max-width: 780px;
    color: #4b5563;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  article {
    padding: 28px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    background: #f8fafc;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
  }

  article h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #111827;
  }

  article p {
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    color: #4b5563;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .callout {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding: 36px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 236, 179, 0.95), rgba(255, 249, 231, 0.95));
    border: 1px solid rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.16);
  }

  .callout h2 {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
  }

  .callout p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #4338ca;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    background: #7c3aed;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    min-width: 180px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .callout {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .callout p {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
